<para>
  <classname>ConstScalarFieldInit</classname> objects are used as
  the <varname>initializer</varname> argument in the <xref
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.Mesh.Set_Field_Initializer"/> command
  when assigning initial values to scalar fields on a &mesh;.  They
  assign the value <varname>value</varname> to the field at all
  points in the &mesh;.
</para>


